          Flash is being killed off

      


        Technology
      

    
    1 hour ago
  


        The software was widespread on the internet in the early part of the last decade, and is used for things like playing videos and games. Adobe announced that it will discontinue the software at the end of 2020.
      

















          Those Splatoon 2 shoes look familiar

      


        Gaming
      

    
    1 hour ago
  


        The Nintendo Switch game appears to pay tribute to Yeezys, the footwear which bears Kanye West's nickname. The virtual swag is one of the most expensive pairs of shoes in the game.
      

















          Senate blocks proposal to repeal Affordable Care Act

      


        Politics
      

    
    5 hours ago
  


        The procedural vote to repeal the ACA failed with a final tally of 43-57. The Senate is expected to vote again Wednesday on new proposals. 
      








